@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
actor "学習者" as Learner
participant "KnowledgeMap" as Map
participant "StaticNodeRepository" as Repo
participant "MotionController" as Motion
participant "NodeDetailPanel" as Detail
participant "LearningHistory" as History

Learner -> Map : ノード選択(nodeId)
Map -> Repo : getNode(nodeId)
Repo --> Map : LearningNode
Map -> Repo : getRelatedEdges(nodeId)
Repo --> Map : KnowledgeEdge[]
Map -> Motion : focusNode(nodeId, relatedEdges)
Motion --> Map : animation plan
Map -> Detail : render(node)
Map -> History : append(nodeId, reasonLabel)
Detail --> Learner : 意図/観察/次の分岐を表示
History --> Learner : 選択履歴を更新
@enduml
